{"tid":2274881,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Fact check 你個 Fact check，103%投票率係絕對有嫌疑的","createTime":"2020-11-06T17:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T10:06:51.000Z","uid":273218,"like":82,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e5dca951f8dbbbd3d60851b5a0511d77e23094b3","tid":2274881,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"聽完蕭山講之後頓開矛塞<br />\n好嬲果班白痴fact  check 洗白撚<br />\n不求甚解就用fact check做武器<br />\n我依家就fact check返佢地個fact check<br />\n其實岩岩睇左加州投票規舉，同埋據蕭山所講<br />\n更新地址係有規舉的<br />\n而班fact check撚完全無提過當中嫌疑<br />\n更新地址前題係要真誠及真係一個月前已搬到當地，所以103%要成立就要證明係大量選民突然搬屋而又無提前更新資料<br />\n其實呢樣野一定有可疑的<br />\n因為如果利用更新漏洞假宣誓<br />\n咁就等於係其他州灌票<br />\n蕭山亦有提灌票係一定犯法的<br />\n所以重點係查90%或103%係咪加州灌過去<br />\n所以可解釋到點解半夜突然多左咁多票<br />\n因為民主黨加州大把票係手<br />\n可以睇住結果來臨時更新地址再郵寄<br />\n正好配合埋有州被捉到back date 選票同埋好遲先寄到票站，甚至係大選截止仍然不斷係其他州灌過去。所以新搬屋果一批選票即是90%-103%係非常嫌疑的，話無問題既真係侮辱人智商<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3ju5Q0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3ju5Q0.jpg&h=f47b690b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b7ee68b523626d3de8da947209c88a9f94b351","tid":2274881,"uid":40628,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"總之左媒話係就等於fact check<br />\n以後TVB 話左膠做咩衰野我都信了"},{"pid":"0f20bae59a8d86442b3ace36d0426d95e621ceea","tid":2274881,"uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"邊個州103%<br />\n<br />\n我呢度有每個州active registered voters既data<br />\n<a href=\"https://worldpopulationreview.com/state-rankings/number-of-registered-voters-by-state\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworldpopulationreview.com%2Fstate-rankings%2Fnumber-of-registered-voters-by-state&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9oR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=20fec1eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://worldpopulationreview.com/state-rankings/number-of-registered-voters-by-state</a><br />\n<br />\n定係你想講county"},{"pid":"f58f01abcbd856721a9596356b